Package cams.users

Class Student

java.lang.Object
cams.users.User
cams.users.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Committable, Enquirer, Serializable
public class Student extends User implements Committable, Enquirer, Serializable
Represents a student, extending User, implementing Committable and Serializable. Students can join committees, register for camps, and interact with camp-related posts.
